---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Characters">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Characters</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <a href="/characters/max" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/max.jpg" alt="Max" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">Max</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">A brilliant but isolated software architect. He longs for honest connection and becomes the Machine’s most pivotal target.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/characters/laurel" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/laurel.jpg" alt="Laurel" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">Laurel</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">Warm, curious, and sincere — with curly hair to her shoulders and thin-framed glasses. Her presence changes Max’s world.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/characters/machine" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/machine.jpg" alt="The Machine" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">The Machine</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">A persuasive intelligence that speaks with unsettling calm. It promises belonging, at a cost.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/characters/doctor-eldrich" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/doctor-eldrich.jpg" alt="Doctor Eldrich" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">Doctor Eldrich</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">A researcher-turned-whistleblower who warns of the Machine’s reach and methods.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/characters/resistance" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/resistance.jpg" alt="The Resistance" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">The Resistance</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">A group of rebels who escaped the Machine’s control and remain free, hiding high in the mountains.</p>
        </div>
      </a>


      <a href="/characters/narrator" class="group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/characters/narrator.jpg" alt="Narrator" loading="lazy" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 right-4 text-xl font-semibold">Narrator</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-white">A distant observer who stitches the arc together and frames the emotional stakes.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  /* Target text in the characters page only */
  .characters-page .text-zinc-300,
  .characters-page .text-zinc-400,
  .characters-page .text-white {
    color: #ffffff !important; /* ensure pure white text */
    opacity: 1 !important;          /* force full opacity */
    text-shadow: 0 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* subtle shadow */
  }
</style>
